quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  111,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  111,1,toot gay abu lahab ke haath aur namuraad ho gaya woh
  111,2,uss ka maal aur jo kuch is ne kamaya woh uss ke kisi kaam nah aaya
  111,3,zaroor woh shola zan aag mein dala jaye ga
  111,4,"aur ( uss ke sath ) uss ki joru bhi, lagai bujhai karne wali"
  111,5,uss ki gardan mein monjh ki rassi hogi
